---
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList.astro";
import PostPreview from "@/components/blog/PostPreview.astro";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import { getAllPosts, sortMDByDate } from "@/data/post";

const MAX_POSTS = 10;
const allPosts = await getAllPosts();
const allPostsByDate = sortMDByDate(allPosts).slice(0, MAX_POSTS);

---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Home" }}>
	<section>
		<h1 class="title mb-6 text-xl">नमस्ते / Hello</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Hey, I'm Prakhar. I'm a designer, interaction developer and a techno-bullish writer. 
			I'm currently pursuing bachelors at IIT Roorkee while also building the design foundation of the <a class="cactus-link" href=https://zk.email/ rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">zkemail</a> ecosystem.
			<h3 class="title mt-8 mb-4 text-xl"> Side Quests</h3>
			<p>
				<h3 class="title mb-2 text-sm"> SDSLabs Joint Secretary</h3>
				Additionally, I also serve as the Joint Secretary and Head of Design of a tech club called <a class="cactus-link" href=https://sdslabs.co/ rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">SDSLabs</a>, 
				here, I lead and learn from the smartest technological builders of IIT R.
			</p>
			<p>
				<h3 class="title mt-4 mb-2 text-sm"> Evolve Network Design Advisor</h3>
				I have also recently joined the design advisory board for <a class="cactus-link" href=https://evolvenetwork.ai/ rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Evolve network</a>, where I guide them build the next generation AI
				products through world class user experience.
			</p>
			<p>
				<h3 class="title mt-4 mb-2 text-sm"> Figma Plugins</h3>
				I also build Figma plugins in my free time, one such plugin is <a class="cactus-link" href=https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/1359544579535199060/auto-pager rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Auto Pager</a>,
				which helps users to streamline documentation. Also, 2 more plugins are in production with release dates in the near foreseeable future.
			</p>
			<h3 class="title mt-8 mb-4 text-xl"> Past Lives</h3>
			<p>
				<h3 class="title mb-2 text-sm"> Noon Dubai [May'24 - Aug'24] - Design Intern </h3>
				I previously worked at <a class="cactus-link" href=https://www.noon.com/uae-en/ rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Noon</a>(Biggest e-commerce player in the Middle-East), where I was the first design intern hire. 
				I still cherish the vivid memories of impacting millions of life, at scale, through my work there.
			</p>
			<p>
				<h3 class="title mt-4 mb-2 text-sm"> Zetpay [Sept'23 - Jan'24] - Cofounder and Head of Design </h3>
				I also tried my hand at building a tech team from scratch.  At Zetpay, I built the complete design foundation. We ultimately grew our team to 7 and demonstrated real-life usecase of UPI for non-Indians.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4">
				Before all this, I designed and developed some kick-ass projects. If you are someone who is interested into my design works <a class="cactus-link" href=https://prakharsingh.framer.website/ rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">this is for you folks.
				</a>
			</p>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<SocialList />
	</section>
	{/* <section  class="mt-16">
		<Inspirations/>
	</section> */}
	<section aria-label="Blog post list" class="mt-16">
		<h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Posts</h2>
		<ul class="space-y-4">
			{
				allPostsByDate.map((p) => (
					<li class="flex flex-col gap-x-2 sm:flex-row">
						<PostPreview post={p} />
					</li>
				))
			}
		</ul>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
